@startuml
autonumber

title Sequence - Student Complaint Submission to Resolution

actor Student
participant "Frontend (React)" as FE
participant "Backend API (Express)" as API
participant "Gemini AI Service" as AI
database "Supabase DB" as DB
collections "Supabase Storage" as ST
participant "Socket.IO" as IO
actor Admin

Student -> FE: Fill complaint form
FE -> API: POST /complaints (multipart, JWT)
API -> ST: Upload image (optional)
ST --> API: image_url
API -> AI: classifyComplaint(description)
AI --> API: ai_priority
API -> DB: Insert complaint(status=pending)
API -> DB: Update asset status=faulty
API -> DB: Insert history('Complaint Logged')
API -> DB: Insert admin notification
API -> IO: emitRoleUpdate('admin', complaint_created)
API -> IO: emitRoleUpdate('student', complaint_created)
API --> FE: 201 complaint
FE --> Student: Show success + realtime refresh

Admin -> FE: Open Kanban board
FE -> API: PATCH /admin/kanban/{id} {status:resolved}
API -> DB: Update complaint status=resolved
API -> DB: Recompute asset status (working/faulty/maintenance)
API -> DB: Insert history('Complaint Resolved')
API -> DB: Insert student notification
API -> IO: emitRoleUpdate('admin', complaint_updated)
API -> IO: emitRoleUpdate('student', complaint_resolved)
API -> IO: emitUserUpdate(reporter, complaint_resolved)
API --> FE: 200 updated complaint
FE --> Admin: Card moved to resolved

IO --> FE: labtrack:update events
FE --> Student: Notification + updated complaint state

@enduml
